  "text": "The D h and size distribution of Doxil® were also measured by DLS at 25°C. This commercial nanoformulation presented a D h of 85.1 ± 0.8 nm, and exhibited a unimodal distribution (Fig. 2) with a PDI value of 0.114 ± 0.002. These values were in good agreement with previous data [CITATION_1] . M.N. Calienni et al. Toxicology and Applied Pharmacology 357 (2018) 106-114 3.2. In vivo toxicity on zebrafish larvae",
